    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for all your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It runs beautifully and still looks great parked in the driveway! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
